Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.68,0:00:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight: Whoo hoo hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.58,0:00:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.08,0:00:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Tada! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.98,0:00:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, Spike. Now\Nlet's try a flip.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.35,0:00:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember, two flaps\Nthen straight up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.92,0:00:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.44,0:00:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're doing great, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.28,0:00:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Now let's see the big finish!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.15,0:00:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahhhhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.76,0:01:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[sigh] I don't know about\Nbig, but I am definitely finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.43,0:01:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should\Nget Rainbow Dash.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.50,0:01:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the one who taught me\Nadvanced flying techniques.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.47,0:01:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.57,0:01:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm going to mess up I'd\Nrather do it in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.27,0:01:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I just don't understand why\Nnone of your advice is helping.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.01,0:01:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Because she's teaching\Nyou to fly like a pony
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.98,0:01:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of a dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.71,0:01:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the difference?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.01,0:01:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we don't have\Nfeathers for starters.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.29,0:01:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah-heh-heh!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.60,0:01:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Thank\Nyou so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.50,0:01:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you know I just\Nneeded to bend my wings?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.37,0:01:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, this is Dragon 101.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.61,0:01:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Usually dragon parents\Nteach this stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.18,0:01:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.98,0:01:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been thinking\Nabout our flying lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.28,0:01:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike: Uh huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.32,0:01:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I overlooked\Nsomething as simple as feathers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.72,0:02:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no wonder you\Nwere having trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.62,0:02:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I had more dragon-ish\Nknowledge to give you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.39,0:02:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think being\Nraised by ponies
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.00,0:02:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,has affected you\Nin other ways?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.03,0:02:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.07,0:02:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say something, Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.84,0:02:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I'm just finishing\Nup this "Thank You"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.80,0:02:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,throw pillow for Smolder.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.07,0:02:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And you know how I get when\NI'm in the embroidery zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.58,0:03:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a pillow. But\Nnot for your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.85,0:03:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Although it could be.\NIt's a throw pillow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.85,0:03:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They're more casual. You\Ncan use them anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.99,0:03:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.09,0:03:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh it's not that. It's just,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.46,0:03:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,dragons don't\Nreally use pillows.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.73,0:03:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,At all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.73,0:03:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.53,0:03:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.13,0:03:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, but it's\NHEADING RIGHT FOR US!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.27,0:03:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,OK. Now I REALLY owe\Nyou for the lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.51,0:03:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh heh. Hey there,\Nyoung dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.62,0:03:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Name's Sludge.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.65,0:03:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,How are your\Ntails shaking?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.05,0:03:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.69,0:03:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.79,0:03:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. What\Nhappened?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.86,0:03:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,To what?\N[crash]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.69,0:03:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.96,0:03:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need to explain myself\Nto a couple of baby dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.67,0:03:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[crash] Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.87,0:04:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe not, but you're\Nhurt and need help,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.48,0:04:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,so I'm taking you to\NTwilight's Castle
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.24,0:04:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,whether you like it or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.15,0:04:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Castle, eh? [moan]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.28,0:04:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad Spike brought\Nyou here, Sludge.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.32,0:04:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand you made quite\Nan impression in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.99,0:04:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Literally. There's a\Nhole and everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.56,0:04:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I hope you're not\Nexpecting me to fix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.10,0:04:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't look like you're\Nin much shape to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.80,0:04:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll manage. Dragons\Ntake care of themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.54,0:04:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need help from a\Nbunch of castle-living ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.48,0:04:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling, do be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.64,0:04:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm [groan] fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.81,0:04:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.22,0:04:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not the first stubborn,\Ndragon we've met, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.42,0:04:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And sometimes even\Ndragons need help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.96,0:04:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise, my friends and\NI will only do enough
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.73,0:04:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,to get you back on your claws.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.59,0:06:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you had\Nyour reservations,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.33,0:06:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's good to see\Nyou feeling better.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.53,0:06:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks? I guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.50,0:06:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what friends\Nare for, darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.50,0:06:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pretty lucky to have\Nfriends like these, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.10,0:06:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually I was orphaned as an\Negg and Twilight raised me,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.84,0:06:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,so these ponies are\Nmore than my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.67,0:06:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,They're my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.76,0:06:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We try our best, but sometimes I\Nworry maybe Spike is--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.55,0:06:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,--missing something deep\Ndown and dragonish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.62,0:06:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.09,0:07:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't tell you how\Nglad I am to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.69,0:07:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Why in Equestria would\Nyou be glad to hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.26,0:07:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't going\Nto say anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.93,0:07:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,since your life\Nseems so perfect,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.06,0:07:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,but I have a\Nconfession to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.67,0:07:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming to Ponyville\Nwasn't an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.27,0:07:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I was looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.74,0:07:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike, [sigh] I'm your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.11,0:07:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.15,0:07:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you crashed in\NPonyville on purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.22,0:07:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the crash part wasn't on\Npurpose, but heading here was.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.59,0:07:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been searching\Neverywhere for you, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.66,0:07:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you ask in the\NCrystal Empire?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.36,0:07:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm kind of well\Nknown there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.16,0:07:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, Spike's\Nwell known everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.46,0:07:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a lot of dragons
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.30,0:07:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,were hatched by the\NPrincess of Friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.63,0:07:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.54,0:07:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You make it sound so simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.70,0:07:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish you'd been there\Nto help me search.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.54,0:07:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.48,0:07:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I have so many questions!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.18,0:08:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, ask away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.48,0:08:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Answering questions\Nis what dads are for!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.85,0:08:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess my biggest\Nquestion is simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.59,0:08:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Why was I an\Norphaned egg?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.66,0:08:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh! You sure you don't wanna\Nask something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.49,0:08:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a lot of painful memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.76,0:08:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother was the best\Ndragon I'd ever met.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.64,0:08:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} The Dragon Lord even{\i0}\N{\i1} picked her to scout for the Great Migration{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.24,0:08:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} and.. and even though she'd{\i0}\N{\i1} just laid your egg,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.54,0:08:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} we knew she'd have to go.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.48,0:08:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} But finding the Migration{\i0}\N{\i1} route could take a lifetime{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.68,0:08:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} and you deserved a chance{\i0}\N{\i1} to know your mother.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.35,0:08:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} So I went looking for her,{\i0}\N{\i1} carried your egg to places{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.72,0:08:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} no dragon, or pony,{\i0}\N{\i1} has ever been.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.59,0:08:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Past Mount Aris, the abandoned{\i0}\N{\i1} home of the Hippogriffs.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.13,0:08:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.10,0:08:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you visit Klugetown?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.83,0:08:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been to Klugetown?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.60,0:08:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,All: Uh huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.00,0:08:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, the Hypogriffs\Nreturned to Mount Aris
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.30,0:08:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,after we helped them\Ndefeat the Storm King.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.27,0:09:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well, have you heard of the\NLand of the.. Scale Collectors?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.41,0:09:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.35,0:09:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Because, that's where your\Nmother's trail finally led
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.72,0:09:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} to a prison world{\i0}\N{\i1} of dragon hunters,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.49,0:09:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} where I was forced{\i0}\N{\i1} to choose between{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.55,0:09:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} surrendering myself or{\i0}\N{\i1} surrendering your egg.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.43,0:09:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Of course, there was no way{\i0}\N{\i1} I was gonna sacrifice my boy,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.76,0:09:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} so they took me instead{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.80,0:09:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} and that's where I've{\i0}\N{\i1} been ever since.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.23,0:09:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Locked up somewhere\Nnot even the
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.80,0:09:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess of Friendship\Nhas heard of.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.34,0:09:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.21,0:09:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you know I was a boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.71,0:09:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What ever happened\Nto Spike's mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.81,0:09:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And how did the egg make it all\Nthe way back to Equestria
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.45,0:09:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,by itself?\N-Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.48,0:09:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I had all the answers!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.04,0:09:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's all\Nin the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.79,0:09:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing that matters\Nnow is that we're together,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.19,0:09:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm gonna make\Nup for lost time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.73,0:09:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you don't mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.90,0:10:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,but I have a list\Nof all the things
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.27,0:10:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I always wanted to\Ndo with my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.20,0:10:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.14,0:10:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike, my boy, with\Nyou by my side,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.91,0:10:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like we can do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.71,0:10:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you\Nwanna do first?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.31,0:10:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I've kind of been working\Non the list for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.38,0:10:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! You wanna do {\i1}all{\i0} of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.65,0:10:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I mean, we\Ndon't have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.86,0:10:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If you think doing everything\Non this incredibly long list
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.56,0:10:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,is gonna fill the hole where\Nyour dragonishness should be,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.97,0:10:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,then that is exactly\Nwhat we're gonna do!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.94,0:10:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.58,0:11:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe we\Ngot so many things done!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.35,0:11:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is all my stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.36,0:11:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anything you\Nalways wanted to do with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.66,0:11:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.40,0:11:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Er.. I-I mean, I'm happy to\Ndo whatever you want,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.50,0:11:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,but.. if I had a castle like\Nthis, with all this stuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.81,0:11:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd probably just\Nlay around all day
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.27,0:11:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,doing nothing like\Na real dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.08,0:11:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a {\i1}real{\i0} dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.88,0:11:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. I'm not surprised\Nyou don't know any better.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.22,0:11:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight basically\Nraised you as a pony.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.22,0:12:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're barely a dragon at all...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.39,0:12:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.89,0:12:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.73,0:12:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,How are things\Ngoing with Sludge?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.60,0:12:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I thought\Nhaving him around
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.90,0:12:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,would make me feel\Nmore dragonish,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.13,0:12:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,but I kinda feel less.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.70,0:12:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh I'm sorry. I wish\NI could help.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.10,0:12:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Sludge: Aw, shucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.24,0:12:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I shouldn't\Nhave said anything
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.21,0:12:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,about you being more\Npony than dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.01,0:12:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wish we had\Nmore in common.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.38,0:12:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you two can come up with\Nways to turn up Spike's..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.29,0:12:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,uh- dragonishness!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.02,0:12:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You think that's\Nsomething we can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.89,0:12:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what, son?\NI think it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.86,0:12:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike, I'm gonna teach\Nyou a thing or two
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.26,0:12:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,about being a dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.83,0:12:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So listen up, my boy, because\NI'm only gonna say this once.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.44,0:12:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Look at this castle{\i0}\N{\i1} where you live! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.31,0:12:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty sweet, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.87,0:12:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ You can't be a dragon here! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.08,0:12:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I can't?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.41,0:13:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Look at these books{\i0}\N{\i1} up on the wall. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.95,0:13:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I just finished\Norganizing those!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.62,0:13:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ This treasure pile's{\i0}\N{\i1} not right, I fear. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.82,0:13:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Trust me, I got ya\Ncovered here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.86,0:13:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You see all this soft, pony\Nstuff you're surrounded with?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.33,0:13:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This has got to be\Nthe first thing to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.93,0:13:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Nothing 'bout this{\i0}\N{\i1} place is dragon den, ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.50,0:13:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ theres too much fluff! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.33,0:13:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ All these fancy{\i0}\N{\i1} robes toss in a pile. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.74,0:13:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Take those goblets,{\i0}\N{\i1} dishes; is that gold? ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.34,0:13:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Still not enough! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.94,0:13:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ De-ponyfying might{\i0}\N{\i1} just take a while. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.58,0:13:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Sure this place{\i0}\N{\i1} is grandiose. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.75,0:13:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ But to a dragon,{\i0}\N{\i1} it's just gross! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.08,0:13:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Time we make the{\i0}\N{\i1} lot all disappear. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.49,0:13:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Reality you need a dose. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.66,0:13:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ To all these ponies{\i0}\N{\i1} you're too close, ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.93,0:13:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ You just can't be a{\i0}\N{\i1} dragon here. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.30,0:13:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job my boy, but this\Nis still just the beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.63,0:13:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Each and every dragon{\i0}\N{\i1} has a swagger of his own, ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.97,0:14:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ watch and I'll show{\i0}\N{\i1} you what I mean! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.57,0:14:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ You can't move like this with{\i0}\N{\i1} so much stuff to way ya down! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.71,0:14:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ A dragon always{\i0}\N{\i1} keeps it lean. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.32,0:14:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Lose this, this,\Nooh this is nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.65,0:14:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Your life is soft, your{\i0}\N{\i1} scales are coiffed. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.72,0:14:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ These pillows, beds{\i0}\N{\i1} and sheets are washed. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.89,0:14:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ A delight but its just not{\i0}\N{\i1} right what's underneath. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.63,0:14:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Every dragon must be free! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.76,0:14:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Look at you, then{\i0}\N{\i1} look at me. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.90,0:14:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Since when do dragons{\i0}\N{\i1} brush their teeth? ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.17,0:14:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hah, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.44,0:14:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Sure this place{\i0}\N{\i1} is grandiose, ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.57,0:14:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ but to a dragon{\i0}\N{\i1} it's just gross! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.87,0:14:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Time we make the{\i0}\N{\i1} lot all disappear! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.08,0:14:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But what do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.08,0:14:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Just grab it all{\i0}\N{\i1} and give to me, ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.55,0:14:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ after that then{\i0}\N{\i1} you'll be free. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.72,0:14:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ You just can't be{\i0}\N{\i1} a dragon... here! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.29,0:14:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hah, you're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.72,0:14:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel better already!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.92,0:14:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,See, what did\NI tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.56,0:14:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're very lucky\Nthat I found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.16,0:14:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Now go get me\Nsome more.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.69,0:14:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.80,0:14:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go get you all the\Ncushy pony stuff I've got...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.33,0:15:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,...Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.17,0:15:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Great, go get 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.83,0:15:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...Son.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.30,0:15:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Cause this dragon just{\i0}\N{\i1} can't wait to live here! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.92,0:15:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[knocking] Spike?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.78,0:15:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I just thought I'd check\Nto see if you and Sludge
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.89,0:15:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,had any luck turning up\Nyour dragonishness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.19,0:15:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard not to\Nfeel like somehow
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.79,0:15:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I let you down\Nall these years.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.49,0:15:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.80,0:15:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean to\Nbarge in on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.50,0:15:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.00,0:15:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Mi castle es su castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.87,0:15:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.... well, I'll just get\Nout of your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.18,0:15:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.55,0:15:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I am so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.58,0:15:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,My morning is not going well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.52,0:15:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What is all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.52,0:15:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd you leave the\NCastle so early?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.49,0:15:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't leave, I spent\Nthe night outdoors
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.56,0:15:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,to get in touch with\Nmy dragon side.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.83,0:16:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Outdoors?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.16,0:16:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! And Sludge\Nasked me to bring him
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.93,0:16:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,the best breakfast\NPonyville has to offer
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.80,0:16:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,so he can show me how\Na real dragon would eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.23,0:16:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later!\N[door slams]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.84,0:16:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why I thought we\Ncould use the map to--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.81,0:16:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, gang.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.98,0:16:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad was just showing me how\Na real dragon would act
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.95,0:16:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,in the throne room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.92,0:16:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragons like to sprawl when\Nthey get their claws done.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.95,0:16:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, if you'll all excuse\Nme, it's time for my bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.66,0:16:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[sigh] Isn't he the best!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.60,0:16:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure that's exactly\Nthe word I would use.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.93,0:16:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Spike?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.10,0:16:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The bath isn't gonna\Nfill itself, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.44,0:16:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Be right there, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.21,0:16:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you're not spending\Nthe night outside again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.68,0:16:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I am. I'm\Njust looking for
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.45,0:16:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,a good bedtime story to\Nread to my dad first.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.92,0:17:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nice that you have somepony\Nto show you dragon culture,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.29,0:17:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,but are you sure that's\Nwhat Sludge is doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.76,0:17:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.66,0:17:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, taking over your room,\Nmaking a mess of things...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.36,0:17:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Pffft.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.13,0:17:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That {\i1}is{\i0} dragon culture.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.07,0:17:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You never acted like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.07,0:17:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because {\i1}you{\i0} raised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.70,0:17:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I finally have a chance\Nto see how I'm supposed to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.24,0:17:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think you're\Nsupposed to be any different
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.21,0:17:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,than who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.61,0:17:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you just don't like\Nthat I have a real parent now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.45,0:17:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.72,0:17:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad Sludge is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.32,0:17:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wish he wasn't such a...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.62,0:17:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon? Of all ponies,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.22,0:17:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe {\i1}you{\i0}\Nwould have a problem with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.36,0:17:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.40,0:17:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.04,0:17:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Just sleeping outside\Nlike we're meant to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.11,0:17:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like dragons are\Nsupposed to live in castles.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.11,0:17:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess not.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.78,0:17:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But I live in\Nthe school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.18,0:18:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing says we {\i1}have{\i0}\Nto live outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.81,0:18:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[sigh] I'm so confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.98,0:18:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been great having Sludge\Nshow me how to be a real dragon,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.89,0:18:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,but Twilight just\Ndoesn't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.09,0:18:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.16,0:18:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She can't handle how good\Nat being a dragon Sludge is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.06,0:18:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe someday I'll be able to\Nlay around doing nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.53,0:18:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,as well as he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.20,0:18:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.03,0:18:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, not now, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.97,0:18:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm too busy bringing\Nhim pony stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.84,0:18:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,so he can show me what a\Ndragon would do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.01,0:18:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Sludge just lays around
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.21,0:18:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,while you wait on\Nhim claw and tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.91,0:18:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, dragons are\Nrude and rebellious,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.48,0:18:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,but they aren't lazy lumps who\Ntake advantage of their kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.15,0:18:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh. Now I'm really confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.69,0:18:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.49,0:18:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you tell me\Neverything Sludge said
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.86,0:18:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,about being a dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.29,0:18:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.23,0:18:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on, son?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.83,0:18:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight doesn't like having\Nreal dragons in the castle
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.63,0:18:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,so I told her we're moving out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.84,0:18:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You what!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.87,0:18:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.84,0:19:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I found the perfect cave\Nwhere you two can live.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.44,0:19:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There aren't even any\Ncomfortable rocks inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.74,0:19:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That does\Nsound perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.51,0:19:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it doesn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.05,0:19:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I-I mean, I'm not sure I've fully\Ndemonstrated all the ways
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.72,0:19:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,a dragon would live here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.79,0:19:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But we're not gonna live here\Nanymore, so it doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.16,0:19:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It matters to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.99,0:19:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I..... I want to make sure you have\Nall the knowledge you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.03,0:19:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.17,0:19:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, you've already\Nshared so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.30,0:19:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ This bed is much too soft. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.34,0:19:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Just take that{\i0}\N{\i1} silk robe off. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.51,0:19:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ We can't be dragons{\i0}\N{\i1} living here! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.18,0:19:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,ARGH! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.15,0:19:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not your father!\N-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.52,0:19:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I just said that to get in\Non this sweet castle life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.86,0:19:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So... you pretended to be my dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.36,0:20:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Na nana. Don't look at\Nme like that, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.83,0:20:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I did what any dragon would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.27,0:20:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.37,0:20:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I saw an opportunity\Nand I took it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.08,0:20:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what dragons do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.21,0:20:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No. It isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.48,0:20:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what? I\Ndon't need this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.05,0:20:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.15,0:20:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Enjoy livin' in pony town...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.19,0:20:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm taking this pillow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.39,0:20:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I thought\Nsomepony like {\i1}that{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.46,0:20:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,could show me how\Nto be.. anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.86,0:20:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[sigh] It must be hard growing up not\Nreally knowing who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.50,0:20:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.90,0:20:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I know exactly who I am,\Nand how I got that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.64,0:20:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.45,0:20:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Hi. Where's\Nyour.. father?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.28,0:20:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.32,0:20:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Turns out he wasn't what a real\Ndragon should be after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.05,0:20:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He also wasn't my real dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.09,0:21:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Spike... I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.43,0:21:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who's sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.20,0:21:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You were just worried about\Nme and I lost my temper.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.06,0:21:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Sludge was just a\Ngreat big phony.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.97,0:21:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to say, I'm not surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.34,0:21:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way a dragon like\Nthat was related to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.47,0:21:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you still want to\Nsearch for your real family,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.94,0:21:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd understand if you spent\Nmore time in the Dragonlands.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.01,0:21:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.15,0:21:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I already know who\Nmy {\i1}real{\i0} family is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.15,0:21:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oooh! It's me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.42,0:21:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm hm! Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.12,0:21:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way I'm\Nliving without pillows.
